  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Told as a Fenrisian saga by a human thrall of the Fang, this is the making of Arjac Rockfist, the Anvil of Fenris and champion of Logan Grimnar. When a tyranid splinter fleet descends on Asaheim itself and the spawn of the great devourer claw their way toward the mountain-fortress of the Space Wolves, it falls to one warrior to hold the line. Between the battles, the saga reaches back through Arjac's humble origins to show how a smith became a legend. As the swarms break against the Fang, Arjac answers the call of destiny with hammer and shield, defending his home world against an enemy that exists only to consume.",
